Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US-Soviet arms talks collapse
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407ccs
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 10 Apr 1977
Warnings over human rights abuses leads to abrupt collapse of SALT talks between US and Russia. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less